RORY MCILROY: Pride.  Just pride.  Just trying to play a good round of golf and try to get something that's close to the best out of myself.  And, yeah, I don't like missing cuts.  It's not something that I'm used to fortunately, and I wanted to be around for the weekend.  And at least if you're around for the weekend, you can go out there and maybe shoot a good one tomorrow and at least give yourself half a chance.
